<h2>Editorial Board Membership Inquiries</h2>

<p>Please contact <strong>edboardmgmt [at] plos.org</strong> if you are interested in joining the <i>PLOS ONE</i> editorial board as an Academic Editor. Our international editorial board is comprised of working scientists who are established principal investigators/group leaders with extensive publication records. Please provide a link to your home page and/or a copy of your Curriculum Vitae (CV) and we will evaluate your suitability and respond in due course.</p>

